Tuchel on not starting Mount in his 1st game: &quot;I have no trust issues but I wanted to give the responsibility in this special moment to more experienced players. There's nothing to worry about, I like his personality.&quot; <br />
<br />
&quot;He cares for Chelsea &amp; gives 100% everytime.&quot;

Thomas Tuchel on Billy Gilmour<br />
<br />
&quot;I have a good impression. He is a very strategic guy, very high level of game understanding, good in the first contact, clever positioning. We will see if he has the physical level. But he is super quick with his feet.&quot;

